snippet.description:
Take the PUMPKIN HEAD CHALLENGE!!! 
Rubberross Please Dance  ►► 9895-0000-003C-F6EE
Subscribe for more GTLive action! ►►http://bit.ly/1Oo7KH9 

You all have been asking for it, so I begin my battle against the Rubberross levels. But Steph and Jason feel I need a bigger challenge. I'm forced to wear a Jack-o-Lantern on my head while playing. For this Halloween it seems that I am the Pumpkin King.

Want more Mario Maker Challenges? Here's a couple to get you started...

Mario Maker Pro Tip Fail! ►► http://bit.ly/20gIuGU
Flappy Mario Maker ►► http://bit.ly/1Ney99d

Subscribe & hang out with us every day! ►►http://bit.ly/1Oo7KH9
Follow us on Twitter at @MatPatGT and #GTLive
snippet.title: GTLive: Mario Maker's Pumpkin Head Challenge
